text: And Manasseh did not drive out <FI>the inhabitants of<Fi> Beth-shean and its towns, nor <FI>of<Fi> Taanach and its towns, nor the inhabitants of Dor and its towns, nor the inhabitants of Ibleam and its towns, nor the inhabitants of Megiddo and its towns; but the Canaanites would dwell in that land.
name: Judges 1:27
